Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:42.17,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}潛力越高 麻煩越大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.29,0:02:47.66,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}dropout mentality 凌駕於非日常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:52.40,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我們帶著一臉睡意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.70,0:02:57.52,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}背後藏著匕首
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:58.02,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}起立！敬禮！鎖定！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:03:02.92,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}曾經想著總有人會解決
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:08.48,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}多少帶著旁觀的心態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:11.16,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}然而
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:16.45,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}Mr.teacher請告訴不成熟的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.49,0:03:21.95,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}何時才能擊倒你這個不落的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:27.45,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}只要挑戰 可能性是half＆half
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:32.44,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}Mr.teacher請看著迷茫的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:37.69,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}為了你比任何人都認真學習
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:43.67,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}殺意就是唯一給你的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:49.22,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}依靠（認真）自己（上吧）革命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:54.26,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}老！師！目標瞄准！
